TopicTitle: Strange symbols on Kerbin in Tracking Station

Articles.Content:
What is this? And where does it come from? Any mod? I have no idea.

It is only on Kerbin tho. And only visible in Tracking Station. And it seems to be dynamic aswell. I had a symbol named "Manley's Abyss", which is now gone.
Ah ok, nvm. They are related to the "FinePrint" contracts mod and involve surveys of these sites.
From the mod FinePrint. Those markers are waypoints from an aerial survey contract.
